# پرامپت قطعی Cursor — ارتقای سیستم AI ماژول محصولات (v3، منطبق‌شده با کد واقعی)

> **هدف:** پیاده‌سازی معماری model-agnostic مبتنی بر key/value، RAG با pgvector، و بهبود دقت AI در ماژول محصولات — بدون تغییر در بقیه سیستم و سازگار با اسکیمای واقعی پروژه.
>
> **وضعیت:** این سند به‌عنوان قانون (Rule) برای Cursor عمل می‌کند. تمام «GROUND TRUTH»‌ها از اسکیما/کد واقعی استخراج و تأیید شده‌اند؛ از آن‌ها تخطی نکن.

---

## 0) دستورالعمل پایه — همیشه

```
You are working on a PRODUCTION Next.js / Prisma / PostgreSQL multi-tenant SaaS
(hundreds of shops, single codebase, row-level isolation by shopId, Farsi RTL UI).

MANDATORY — read fully before ANY change:
- prisma/schema.prisma
- src/lib/openrouter-fetch.ts
- src/lib/rate-limiter.ts
- src/lib/parse-ai-json.ts
- src/lib/validate-ai-output.ts
- src/lib/validate-ai-request.ts
- src/app/api/admin/products/ai-control/route.ts
- src/app/api/super-admin/settings/route.ts
- src/app/super-admin/page.tsx

GROUND TRUTH (تأییدشده از اسکیما/کد — اشتباه نکن):
- `SystemSetting` = KEY/VALUE table { key String @id, value String }. NO columns.
  Models live as ROWS. Existing keys: openrouter_model, openrouter_control_model,
  openrouter_blog_model, openrouter_api_key, ai_enabled, pexels_api_key, poof_api_key.
- `ShopSettings` is fetched by `shopId` (@unique), never by `id`. DB column is "shop_id".
- `Product` field is `title` (NOT name). It has NO tags/sku/discountedPrice/reservedStock.
  It HAS: title, description, price, discount, stock, brand, categoryId,
  wholesalePrice, wholesaleTiers, wholesaleExclusivePrices, moq, wholesaleUnit,
  wholesaleUnitSize, isWholesaleOnly, isActive, isSpecial, specialEndsAt.
- Raw SQL → use Prisma.sql / Prisma.empty from '@prisma/client'. `prisma.$raw` DOES NOT EXIST.
- Existing helpers (use, don't duplicate):
  isRateLimited(shopId, limit=20, windowMs=60000) → already 20/min per shop.
  parseAiJson<T>(raw, requiredFields, fallback) → truncation-safe.
  validators.product(data) → checks price/stock/discountPercent only.
  openRouterFetch(url, options) → retry+backoff for chat/completions.
  getIranDateTime() → live Tehran date/time.

GLOBAL RULES:
1. Surgical changes only. No unrelated refactor. No file/folder renames. No new packages.
2. Every DB query scoped by shopId. No exceptions.
3. Every async side-effect has .catch(). Side-effects never block or crash the main flow.
4. Keep existing system prompts intact — ADD only, never replace.
5. Phase 1 → migrate → test → only then Phase 2. Report what changed and why after each step.
```

